1
00:01:07,480 --> 00:01:09,400
I was just too scared.

2
00:01:10,560 --> 00:01:12,000
I just wanted to hurry back here to hide.

3
00:01:14,519 --> 00:01:15,920
How did you open this keypad door?

4
00:01:16,519 --> 00:01:17,879
Didn't you tell me you didn't know?

5
00:01:20,599 --> 00:01:22,079
I just remembered.

6
00:01:22,640 --> 00:01:24,959
My older sister mentioned it in an email she left me.

7
00:01:25,799 --> 00:01:26,480
At a time like this,

8
00:01:26,599 --> 00:01:27,799
you're still not telling me the truth.

9
00:01:39,239 --> 00:01:39,799
Xiao Ran

10
00:01:41,040 --> 00:01:41,519
Come here, quick

11
00:01:41,920 --> 00:01:43,000
Look what I found

12
00:01:47,920 --> 00:01:48,359
Money

13
00:01:48,640 --> 00:01:50,040
Finally, I can buy a new pair of shoes

14
00:01:50,200 --> 00:01:51,519
And I can take you to eat boat noodles

15
00:01:52,640 --> 00:01:53,400
Boat noodles

16
00:01:53,560 --> 00:01:55,400
Boat noodles? I want some, Sister

17
00:01:59,079 --> 00:02:00,319
I'll take you to eat right now

18
00:02:00,480 --> 00:02:01,239
But, Xiao Ran

19
00:02:01,719 --> 00:02:03,879
You must not tell Mom and Dad we found money

20
00:02:04,200 --> 00:02:05,200
You absolutely can't say a word

21
00:02:08,319 --> 00:02:09,560
I'll fight you to the death today! You dare hit me?

22
00:02:09,919 --> 00:02:10,840
I'll kill you

23
00:02:11,000 --> 00:02:11,479
Sister

24
00:02:12,360 --> 00:02:14,319
Let's just tell Mom and Dad

25
00:02:14,800 --> 00:02:17,479
Otherwise they'll keep fighting

26
00:02:18,319 --> 00:02:20,120
No, we absolutely can't tell them

27
00:02:21,879 --> 00:02:22,879
Mom

28
00:02:24,039 --> 00:02:25,520
Mom

29
00:02:28,039 --> 00:02:30,960
Mom, don't leave us behind

30
00:02:31,199 --> 00:02:32,680
Don't leave me

31
00:02:32,800 --> 00:02:34,560
Xiao Ran, listen to Mom

32
00:02:34,680 --> 00:02:36,080
Mom will be back very soon

33
00:02:36,319 --> 00:02:38,319
Then I'll buy you lots and lots of new clothes

34
00:02:38,560 --> 00:02:39,759
And lots and lots of toys

35
00:02:40,000 --> 00:02:41,759
And take you to eat delicious food, okay?

36
00:02:42,159 --> 00:02:43,599
Don't cry now, listen to Mom

37
00:02:44,800 --> 00:02:45,800
Really?

38
00:02:50,639 --> 00:02:51,800
Mom

39
00:02:52,439 --> 00:02:54,800
Don't leave us behind

40
00:03:00,240 --> 00:03:01,439
Mom

41
00:03:02,520 --> 00:03:04,800
Don't go, Mom

42
00:03:08,560 --> 00:03:10,159
Mom

43
00:03:11,560 --> 00:03:13,039
Did you steal my money?

44
00:03:13,439 --> 00:03:13,840
Speak!

45
00:03:14,520 --> 00:03:15,919
Don't hit Sister anymore

46
00:03:16,280 --> 00:03:17,280
Don't hit Sister anymore

47
00:03:17,520 --> 00:03:18,319
Speak up, you!

48
00:03:18,919 --> 00:03:20,360
I took the money

49
00:03:20,520 --> 00:03:22,120
Sister didn't take it

50
00:03:23,560 --> 00:03:24,800
So you were in on it too

51
00:03:28,039 --> 00:03:29,759
I... I'll beat you to death

52
00:03:32,680 --> 00:03:33,520
Stealing money, huh?

53
00:03:33,879 --> 00:03:34,680
Stealing money!

54
00:03:35,199 --> 00:03:36,319
Stealing my money!

55
00:03:43,680 --> 00:03:44,560
Sister

56
00:03:44,840 --> 00:03:46,879
Sister, where are you going?

57
00:03:47,159 --> 00:03:48,919
Don't leave me behind

58
00:03:50,719 --> 00:03:52,680
Don't leave me behind

59
00:03:53,439 --> 00:03:55,319
Don't leave me behind

60
00:03:55,560 --> 00:03:56,199
Xiao Ran

61
00:03:57,879 --> 00:03:59,120
Sister doesn't want to leave either

62
00:04:00,360 --> 00:04:01,280
Sister promises

63
00:04:01,719 --> 00:04:02,280
In the future

64
00:04:02,759 --> 00:04:03,759
I will definitely take you to live

65
00:04:03,879 --> 00:04:05,400
in the place closest to the sky

66
00:04:06,400 --> 00:04:07,919
in a house like a castle

67
00:04:08,919 --> 00:04:09,719
When that time comes

68
00:04:10,479 --> 00:04:11,759
we'll have endless money

69
00:04:13,280 --> 00:04:14,639
and never go hungry again

70
00:04:20,680 --> 00:04:21,480
Damn brats

71
00:04:21,720 --> 00:04:22,519
Trying to run?

72
00:04:23,360 --> 00:04:24,800
Believe it or not, I'll break your legs

73
00:04:25,600 --> 00:04:26,839
Money... where is my money?

74
00:04:26,959 --> 00:04:27,920
Leave the money before you go

75
00:04:28,920 --> 00:04:29,920
We don't have money

76
00:04:30,199 --> 00:04:31,399
You took all the money to buy booze

77
00:04:31,519 --> 00:04:32,079
No money?

78
00:04:32,759 --> 00:04:34,639
If there's no money, I'll sell you one by one

79
00:04:37,600 --> 00:04:38,040
Crying

80
00:04:38,519 --> 00:04:39,480
All you know is how to cry

81
00:04:39,759 --> 00:04:40,720
I'll sell you first

82
00:04:41,600 --> 00:04:42,680
Don't touch my younger sister

83
00:04:42,959 --> 00:04:44,040
You ruined this family

84
00:04:44,560 --> 00:04:45,560
I hate you

85
00:04:46,279 --> 00:04:46,720
Go

86
00:04:47,240 --> 00:04:47,879
Stop

87
00:04:48,600 --> 00:04:49,199
Stop

88
00:04:50,360 --> 00:04:51,519
You two stop right there

89
00:04:52,160 --> 00:04:52,600
Run

90
00:04:53,040 --> 00:04:54,000
Trying to run?

91
00:04:54,759 --> 00:04:55,600
Stop

92
00:04:59,279 --> 00:05:00,079
Wait for me to come back

93
00:05:00,319 --> 00:05:01,839
Where can you run to?

94
00:05:02,639 --> 00:05:03,279
Come back

95
00:05:08,439 --> 00:05:09,800
Little Ren, Xiao Ran

96
00:05:10,879 --> 00:05:12,439
Regarding your father's death

97
00:05:12,759 --> 00:05:14,000
Auntie is deeply sorry

98
00:05:14,639 --> 00:05:16,600
Since we can't contact your mom

99
00:05:16,920 --> 00:05:18,720
the community contacted us

100
00:05:20,759 --> 00:05:21,399
Today

101
00:05:21,600 --> 00:05:23,240
Auntie is here to take you to a new home

102
00:05:23,399 --> 00:05:24,439
Hongshan Welfare Agency

103
00:05:25,000 --> 00:05:26,759
You will live there for a while

104
00:05:28,399 --> 00:05:29,800
The welfare agency will find for you

105
00:05:29,959 --> 00:05:30,959
new moms and dads

106
00:05:31,399 --> 00:05:33,199
so you can have your own home again

107
00:05:34,240 --> 00:05:35,560
Then can we go to school?

108
00:05:37,040 --> 00:05:37,759
Of course

109
00:06:04,879 --> 00:06:05,560
Xiao Ran

110
00:06:07,199 --> 00:06:08,319
I heard from Auntie Zhang

111
00:06:08,519 --> 00:06:10,759
that a very good family has taken a liking to you.

112
00:06:11,000 --> 00:06:12,519
They might adopt you.

113
00:06:13,639 --> 00:06:14,600
Listen to your big sister.

114
00:06:15,199 --> 00:06:16,439
You must be very well-behaved.

115
00:06:16,720 --> 00:06:17,720
Very obedient.

116
00:06:18,040 --> 00:06:19,240
You must go with them.

117
00:06:20,120 --> 00:06:21,720
What about you, sister?

118
00:06:23,560 --> 00:06:24,279
Don't worry.

119
00:06:24,399 --> 00:06:25,079
Wherever you go,

120
00:06:25,199 --> 00:06:27,279
I will find you and protect you.

121
00:06:27,600 --> 00:06:28,519
For the rest of my life.

122
00:06:34,920 --> 00:06:36,720
I want my sister.

123
00:06:36,920 --> 00:06:39,199
I want to go home.

124
00:06:42,600 --> 00:06:45,160
I want to go home.

125
00:06:51,519 --> 00:06:52,079
Little sister.

126
00:06:53,160 --> 00:06:54,480
Don't forget our promise.

127
00:06:55,560 --> 00:06:57,199
I know you are sisters who shared hardships.

128
00:06:58,079 --> 00:06:58,480
All these years,

129
00:06:58,639 --> 00:06:59,800
you've been in contact, right?

130
00:07:04,040 --> 00:07:05,000
We're in contact.

131
00:07:06,079 --> 00:07:07,000
What does that prove?

132
00:07:07,160 --> 00:07:08,399
It proves you're close.

133
00:07:08,959 --> 00:07:09,959
But you're still lying.

134
00:07:11,160 --> 00:07:13,000
This must be related to the money.

135
00:07:13,959 --> 00:07:14,800
This money...

136
00:07:16,839 --> 00:07:18,079
I legally inherited it.

137
00:07:18,240 --> 00:07:21,319
All my sister and brother-in-law's cash and property.

138
00:07:22,399 --> 00:07:23,600
From a legal standpoint,

139
00:07:24,480 --> 00:07:25,639
this money is all mine.

140
00:07:27,319 --> 00:07:28,920
This money was obtained illegally.

141
00:07:29,040 --> 00:07:30,040
It will be confiscated.

142
00:07:30,240 --> 00:07:30,920
Don't move.

143
00:07:33,040 --> 00:07:33,720
Li Ren.

144
00:07:35,240 --> 00:07:36,360
Just as I expected.

145
00:07:38,839 --> 00:07:39,680
You're still alive.

146
00:07:43,240 --> 00:07:44,680
I know you're a victim too.

147
00:07:45,399 --> 00:07:46,920
You've suffered a lot all these years.

148
00:07:47,920 --> 00:07:49,920
If you're willing to turn yourself in and testify against Tan Tian...

149
00:07:50,120 --> 00:07:51,439
I will plead for leniency for you in court.

150
00:07:51,879 --> 00:07:53,120
I can't turn back.

151
00:07:54,519 --> 00:07:55,720
Have you thought about her?

152
00:07:58,639 --> 00:07:59,680
Is she not important to you?

153
00:08:00,279 --> 00:08:01,879
You've protected her all these years.

154
00:08:02,800 --> 00:08:04,399
Now you're dragging her into crime.

155
00:08:05,639 --> 00:08:06,680
Her life is ruined.

156
00:08:07,920 --> 00:08:08,720
Doesn't your heart ache?

157
00:08:08,879 --> 00:08:10,759
I did everything alone.

158
00:08:11,319 --> 00:08:12,360
It has nothing to do with her.

159
00:08:13,240 --> 00:08:14,600
Saying it has nothing to do with her now...

160
00:08:15,399 --> 00:08:16,000
is too late.

161
00:08:18,000 --> 00:08:18,839
Honestly,

162
00:08:18,959 --> 00:08:21,040
this is the topic our family least wants to bring up.

163
00:08:21,399 --> 00:08:24,160
You mean Li Ran's past?

164
00:08:26,399 --> 00:08:27,079
Why?

165
00:08:29,279 --> 00:08:30,000
Because...

166
00:08:30,360 --> 00:08:32,600
a lot of unpleasant things happened back then.

167
00:08:33,759 --> 00:08:35,519
They were all related to that sister of hers.

168
00:08:37,840 --> 00:08:39,919
They've been in contact behind our backs.

169
00:08:41,320 --> 00:08:42,039
Of course,

170
00:08:42,559 --> 00:08:43,799
if it was just contact,

171
00:08:43,960 --> 00:08:45,279
we wouldn't have any objection.

172
00:08:46,879 --> 00:08:47,639
But...

173
00:08:53,039 --> 00:08:53,519
Li Ran.

174
00:08:55,679 --> 00:08:57,360
Your sister has been secretly protecting you.

175
00:08:58,519 --> 00:08:59,600
She even... for your sake,

176
00:09:01,320 --> 00:09:02,240
almost killed someone.

177
00:09:02,679 --> 00:09:03,240
Right?

178
00:09:08,159 --> 00:09:08,679
Hello, Sis.

179
00:09:10,240 --> 00:09:11,720
I'm almost there. I'm on my way.

180
00:09:12,480 --> 00:09:13,720
Okay, bye.

181
00:09:16,200 --> 00:09:18,320
Which old lover are you talking to?

182
00:09:19,919 --> 00:09:20,720
Give me back my phone.

183
00:09:21,399 --> 00:09:22,799
It was you, you witch.

184
00:09:23,039 --> 00:09:24,440
You snitched to the teacher,

185
00:09:24,720 --> 00:09:26,519
saying I bullied and robbed you, right?

186
00:09:26,879 --> 00:09:27,840
I'll tell you one more time.

187
00:09:28,399 --> 00:09:29,200
Give me back my phone.

188
00:09:29,440 --> 00:09:30,519
I knew it was you.

189
00:09:30,840 --> 00:09:32,759
Relying on your family's little power and status,

190
00:09:32,879 --> 00:09:34,440
to find trouble with me for no reason.

191
00:09:35,559 --> 00:09:36,600
But don't forget,

192
00:09:37,120 --> 00:09:38,840
my dad has some power too.

193
00:09:39,120 --> 00:09:39,960
You...

194
00:09:42,080 --> 00:09:42,960
Who in school doesn't know?

195
00:09:43,080 --> 00:09:44,799
You're an adopted bastard.

196
00:09:45,399 --> 00:09:46,919
Today, on behalf of your parents,

197
00:09:47,080 --> 00:09:48,320
I'm going to teach you a good lesson.
